# Power BI Dashboard Structure

## Page 1: Overview
- Total Customers
- Total Transactions
- Total Amount
- Line Chart: Transactions Over Time

## Page 2: Customer Insights
- Income vs Spend (Scatter Plot)
- Top Customers (Bar Chart)
- Filters: Location, Account Type

## Page 3: Risk Analysis
- Risk Levels (Pie Chart)
- Loan Status (Bar Chart)
- High Risk Customers Table

## Page 4: Fraud Detection
- Transactions by Device
- Suspicious Transactions (Amount > 15000)
- Transaction Trends